    • Constructor Detail

      • AttackPattern

        public AttackPattern(java.lang.String protocol,
                     java.lang.String ipAddress,
                     int port,
                     int threadAmount,
                     int connectionTimeOut,
                     int attackRange,
                     java.lang.String message,
                     java.lang.String additionalInformation)
        The attack pattern object constructor. It receives a protocol, target ip address, target connection port, thread amount used by DDOS attack, connection time out of socket, attack shot range, a text message end any additional information and sets these parameters in object attributes.
        Parameters:
        protocol - THe protocol that will be used by DDOS attack.
        ipAddress - The string target IP address.
        port - A integer target port value.
        threadAmount - A integer thread amount of attack.
        connectionTimeOut - A integer connection time out of sockets created.
        attackRange - The attack shots time range.
        message - A text message that will be send by zombie host.
        additionalInformation - Any additional text information field.
